  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Woodlands<br /><br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong><br />Monday to Saturday | 8:30am – 6:30pm</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong><br />Vegetable & Fruit Wholesale / Distribution Company</p><h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Transport and deliver vegetables and fruits to designated locations</p></li><li><p>Ensure goods are delivered safely and on time</p></li><li><p>Assist with basic loading and unloading of goods</p></li><li><p>Maintain vehicle cleanliness and perform basic daily vehicle checks</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Possess a valid Singapore <strong>Class 4 driving licence</strong></p></li><li><p>Responsible, punctual, and reliable</p></li><li><p>Able to commit to long-term employment</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Additional Information</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Candidates with relevant delivery or logistics experience are encouraged to apply</p></li><li><p>Stable working environment provided</p></li></ul><p><br /><br />EA Personnel Name: ZOE ZHANG ZIJUN</p><p>Registration NO.: R23116173</p><p>EA Licence NO.: 13C6639</p>",
